General.Name: Ispac 1 Ltd
General.Description: ISPAC 1 LTD. does not have significant operations. It intends to identify and evaluate assets or businesses with a view to complete a qualifying transaction. The company was formerly known as B1Spack Ltd. and changed its name to ISPAC 1 LTD. in June 2021. ISPAC 1 LTD. was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Givatayim, Israel.
